{"tid":810844,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找錶鄉的故事 非曬命 有圖","createTime":"2018-09-08T10:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T12:37:28.000Z","uid":51269,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b79b1d61e305ae586b5c8575ae4becc1cc53fed8","tid":810844,"uid":51269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"如題 近日睇到篇有關錶既文章 突然心血來潮想追查隻錶既來歷 但係奈隻錶logo都冇 <br />\n所以想睇下各位絲巴打金精火眼睇得出依隻錶係咩牌子<br />\n感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資料：<br />\n日本 神戶購物街店買<br />\n應該係石英錶<br />\n初步估計可能係d業餘工藝師既手作<br />\n可能係cheap野 所以應該追尋到既機會好細<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235146_76c3d7a233a8ec2578d2cba3c0f6e3eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235146_76c3d7a233a8ec2578d2cba3c0f6e3eb.jpg&h=143c908a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235147_548acc0252f748fdf5e37d58a29a8756.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235147_548acc0252f748fdf5e37d58a29a8756.jpg&h=28ad8fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/235149_eaf0c6b1157225058c79fe3b8210fbdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F235149_eaf0c6b1157225058c79fe3b8210fbdf.jpg&h=ad09a2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n非曬命 純心血來潮 想知道佢既來歷<br />\n感激各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"5293e8558a4301839633558e6bf5f3fb2fcab2bf","tid":810844,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"失敗左啦[/quote]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0518170d5